# Local SQLite databases — factory's runtime state lives in a repo-local
# `.factory/` (see below) or `~/.factory/` fallback; neither should be
# committed.
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# Repo-local factory instance — holds config.toml (Discord + Telegram bot
# tokens), factory.db (spend history + directives), and logs/. NEVER commit
# — one `git add -A` would leak tokens to git history.
.factory/

notes.md

